OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FA man accused of killing two police
OL,7,Fofficers in Australia and seriously
OL,8,Fwounding a third has been shot dead by
OL,9,Fofficers following a seven-month
OL,10,Fmanhunt.
OL,12,FDezi Freeman, 56, allegedly opened
OL,13,Ffire on police officers who came to
OL,14,Fserve a warrant at his home near
OL,15,FPorepunkah, in the Victoria state
OL,16,Fnortheast of Melbourne, on August 26
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
