PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FFreeman had not been seen since. On
OL,7,FMonday, a man believed to be Freeman
OL,8,Fwas fatally shot by police following a
OL,9,Fthree-hour standoff at a remote
OL,10,Flocation near Thologolong in the north
OL,11,Fof the state, Victoria's police chief
OL,12,FMike Bush said.
OL,14,F"We believe it is Freeman, but we have
OL,15,Fto go through a formal identification
OL,16,Fprocess," Bush told reporters in
OL,17,FMelbourne.
OL,19,FIdentification could take up to 48
OL,20,Fhours through processes including
OL,21,Ffingerprinting, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
