OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"This was all about bringing this to a
OL,12,Fconclusion as safely as possible,"
OL,13,FBush continued.
OL,15,F"Our ultimate goal was to arrest the
OL,16,Fperson there ... as peacefully as
OL,17,Fpossible."
OL,26,@sD@AOU
