PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FHeavily armed Special Operations Group
OL,7,Ftactical police were involved in the
OL,8,Fstand off, and it was "strongly
OL,9,Fbelieved" Freeman was armed, Bush said.
OL,11,FFreeman had been inside a shelter like
OL,12,Fa shipping container and did take up a
OL,13,Fpolice offer to surrender, he added.
OL,15,FDetective Leading Senior Constable
OL,16,FNeal Thompson, 59, and Senior
OL,17,FConstable Vadim De Waart, 35, of
OL,18,FVictoria Police, were allegedly killed
OL,19,Fby Freeman while executing a search
OL,20,Fwarrant last year.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
