PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FThompson had been just days away from
OL,7,Fretiring when he was killed, Victoria
OL,8,FPolice said.
OL,10,FThe officers had been executing a
OL,11,Fsearch warrant as part of an
OL,12,Finvestigation by the Wangaratta Sexual
OL,13,FOffences and Child Abuse Investigation
OL,14,FTeam.
OL,16,FThe families of the officers killed
OL,17,Fwere the first to be told about
OL,18,FFreeman's death, Bush said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
