PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FFreeman had fled the scene alone, on
OL,7,Ffoot and armed, into the surrounding
OL,8,Fforest after the shooting.
OL,10,FOfficers believe Freeman had
OL,11,Fassistance in hiding, and an
OL,12,Finvestigation will now try and
OL,13,Fidentify anyone who helped him, Bush
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"If anyone was complicit, they will be
OL,17,Fheld accountable," he told reporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
