CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774908661
OL,3,CSuspect who killed Australia policemen
OL,4,Cshot dead in 3-hour stand off
OL,6,FAustralian news outlets widely
OL,7,Freported that Freeman, also known as
OL,8,FDesmond Filby, had co-called sovereign
OL,9,Fcitizen beliefs, meaning he rejected
OL,10,Fthe police and law.
OL,12,FHe had wilderness survival skills that
OL,13,Fpolice feared could sustain him living
OL,14,Fin the open indefinitely.
OL,16,FBush would not say whether a tipoff
OL,17,Fled police to the suspect on Monday,
OL,18,Fas a 1 million Australian dollar
OL,19,F(about #517,430) reward for
OL,20,Finformation had been issued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
